<sec>
<st>
 Security features <ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%222%22])">2</ref></st>
<p>

<image location="right" width="255px" src="500-1991a.jpg" type="thumb">
<caption>

