Obverse of the 1994 first series banknote
</caption>
</image>

<image location="right" width="255px" src="500-1994b.jpg" type="thumb">
<caption>

Reverse of the 1994 first series banknote
</caption>
</image>

<image location="right" width="255px" src="500-1996a.jpg" type="thumb">
<caption>

Obverse of the 1996 first series banknote
</caption>
</image>

<image location="right" width="255px" src="500-1996b.jpg" type="thumb">
